select `idProjet`, `dateDebut`, `idEtp`, `dateFin`, `module_name`, `etp_name`, `li_name`, `ville`, `project_status`, `project_reference`, `project_description`, `project_type`, `paiement`, DATE_FORMAT(dateDebut, "%M, %Y") AS headDate, `module_image`, `etp_logo`, `etp_initial_name`, `idSalle`, `salle_name`, `salle_quartier`, `salle_code_postal`, `ville`, `idCfp_inter`, `modalite`, `total_ht`, `total_ttc`, `idModule`, `project_inter_privacy`, `sub_name`, `idSubContractor`, `idCfp`, `cfp_name`, `headYear`, `headMonthDebut`, `headMonthFin`, `headDayDebut`, `headDayFin`, `total_ht_sub_contractor` from `v_projet_cfps` where ((`idCfp` = 2 or `idCfp_inter` = 2 or `idSubContractor` = 2)) and `project_status` = 'En cours' group by `idProjet` order by `dateDebut` asc
select `dossiers`.`idDossier`, `nomDossier` from `dossiers` inner join `projets` on `dossiers`.`idDossier` = `projets`.`idDossier` where `idProjet` = 400

select COUNT(d.idDocument) as document_count from `documents` as `d` inner join `dossiers` as `ds` on `ds`.`idDossier` = `d`.`idDossier` inner join `projets` as `p` on `ds`.`idDossier` = `p`.`idDossier` where `p`.`idProjet` = 400 limit 1

select `idSeance`, `dateSeance`, `heureDebut`, `id_google_seance`, `heureFin`, `idSalle`, `idProjet`, `salle_name`, `salle_quartier`, `project_title`, `project_description`, `idModule`, `module_name`, `ville` from `v_seances` where `idProjet` = 400

select `idFormateur`, `name` as `form_name`, `firstName` as `form_firstname`, `photoForm` as `form_photo`, `initialNameForm` as `form_initial_name` from `v_formateur_cfps` where `idProjet` = 400 group by `idFormateur`, `name`, `firstName`, `photoForm`, `initialNameForm`
select count(*) as aggregate from `v_list_apprenants` where `idProjet` = 400
select SUM(project_price_pedagogique + project_price_annexe) AS project_total_price from `v_projet_cfps` where `idProjet` = 400 limit 1
select IFNULL(TIME_FORMAT(SEC_TO_TIME(SUM(TIME_TO_SEC(intervalle_raw))), '%H:%i'), '0') as sumHourSession from `v_seances` where `idProjet` = 400 limit 1
select `idProjet` from `eval_chauds`
select `idProjet`, `idEmploye`, `generalApreciate` from `v_evaluation_alls` where `idProjet` = 400 group by `idProjet`, `idEmploye`
select SUM(generalApreciate) as generalNote from `v_general_note_evaluation` where `idProjet` = 400 limit 1

select `idEtp`, `etp_name`, `etp_logo`, `etp_initial_name` from `v_projet_cfps` where `idProjet` = 400 and not `idEtp` = 2 group by `idEtp`, `etp_name`, `etp_logo`, `etp_initial_name`
select `idRestauration`, `paidBy` from `project_restaurations` where `idProjet` = 400
